data.title: Raising Victor Vargas
data.text:
Victor asks his friend Harold, “You crazy?” (0:07)

Judy tells her friend Melonie, referring to some rude guys, “If either one of us gets with a guy like that, I’m gonna shoot myself.”

Melonie: ”Well, I’ll shoot myself too.” (0:09)

Victor tells Grandma, referring to his sister Vicki, “She’s crazy.” (0:11)

Victor asks Judy’s brother Carlos, “Are you crazy?... She’s... retarded...” (0:17)

Victor tells Judy, “I mean, I guess you wouldn’t know how it feels to get nervous around certain people.” (0:19)

Victor tells his brother Nino, “It’s like an instinct...” (0:28)

Vicki tells Nino, “Victor’s such a... compulsive liar.” (0:30)

Vicki tells Victor, “What a... idiot you are.” (0:32)

Victor asks Carlos, “You crazy?” (0:32)

Vicki tells Carlos, “You’re like a stalker.” (0:47)

Victor tells Judy he invite her to his home “... because I wanted you to meet my crazy ma...” (1:12)
